description: Killer Melts is a scrumptious Miami truck bringing cheesy goodness to the streets of South Florida one sandwich at a time! With a wide range of melts, from bacon to short ribs, and many delicious fry options from pork or blue cheese to your classic poutine, Killer Melts has you covered on all your delicious cheesy food choices. If you're in need of a pick-me-up, or just want to make a good day better, check out Killer Melts today!
name: Killer Melts
